+# User Action Feature Implementation
 
-</div>
+## Summary
+
+This implementation adds **User Action** functionality to Anki-Android, enabling users to trigger custom JavaScript functions from the review screen using keyboards, gestures, or external devices (e.g., gamepads). This feature is similar to AnkiMobile's user action functionality.
+
+## Quick Start
+
+### What You CAN Do
 
-Install
----------
-<div style="display:flex;">
+1. **Define JavaScript functions** in your card templates:
+   ```javascript
+   function revealNext() {
+       // Reveal the next cloze deletion
+   }
+   ```
 
